    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“<strong>シシテナオ</strong>-Even in Death”是一款需要不断试误的潜行恐怖动作游戏。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 推荐给玩家</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏非常适合那些想要通过谨慎的潜行游戏来享受紧张感的玩家。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 故事。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏讲述一个少女在一个阴森且诡异的世界里醒来，在那里被称为‘陷人（Ochibito）’的生物在街上游荡。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 潜行动作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“SHI SHI TE NA O-Even in Death”是一款需要完美潜行的动作游戏。在异形的存在「陷人（オチビト）」徘徊的世界中，您需要抑制脚步声、蹲下隐藏并屏住呼吸小心行动。深入理解「陷人」的特性，并观察他们的动向，谨慎行事是生存的关键。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/96c96be5dfe2c2311bb60f33adeccfc1.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/96c96be5dfe2c2311bb60f33adeccfc1.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 世界观。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2D 背景、恐怖的怪物怪异地到处奔跑、敌人从后面出现、阴森的说话声音和音效，再加上整个游戏中不稳定的氛围，总让玩家产生紧张的感觉。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/7792cc6709521b4d20cab7c641fde965.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/7792cc6709521b4d20cab7c641fde965.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/d7eb3b2926deef0113537c798b6d2300.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/d7eb3b2926deef0113537c798b6d2300.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由於音效对了解敌人的位置与动作至关重要，我们强烈建议使用耳机进行游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作以 <strong>Full HD</strong> 制作而成。若在分辨率高于 <strong>Full HD</strong> 的显示器上全屏游玩，可能会出现锯齿现象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏使用 <strong>《动作游戏制作大师MV》</strong> 制作。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※若游戏无法启动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安装 <strong>Steam</strong> 上的 <strong>《动作游戏制作大师MV》</strong> 体验版，可能会补齐计算机所需的 <strong>DLL</strong> 文件，从而使游戏顺利运行。</p>",
